comment: Clean benzene - active (activity cliff with next)
Clean toluene - inactive (activity cliff - similar structure big activity diff)
S-stereoisomer - inactive (stereo pair 1 - activity cliff due to stereochem)
Methyl vinyl ketone Michael acceptor PAINS
Very long chain - low activity (lipophilicity issue)
Hydrocinnamic acid - active (activity cliff with next)
Phenylbutyric acid - inactive (one extra CH2 = big drop)
Lauric acid - long chain low activity
